Package com.vangav.backend.cassandra.keyspaces_generator

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CassandraGeneratorConstantsInl
    GeneratorConstants contains constants shared by all generators (e.g.: keyspaces directory path, etc ...)
    CassandraVerifierInl
    CassandraVerifierInl has inline static methods for verifying keyspaces config files [*.keyspace]
    CqlScriptsGeneratorInl
    PhrictionGeneratorInl generates CQL scripts for creating Cassandra's keyspaces and tables.
    JavaClientGeneratorInl
    JavaClientGeneratorMain generates JAVA clients for Cassandra.
    KeyspacesUpdaterMain
    KeyspacesUpdaterMain is used to update a backend's database (JAVA clients, CQL scripts and phriction wiki).
    PhrictionGeneratorInl
    PhrictionGeneratorInl generates phabricator phriction's (wiki) formatted text for Cassandra's keyspaces, tables, columns, queries, descriptions, etc ...
